				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">the argument that casual players shouldn't be rewarded with gear like hardcore raiding folks get is a bit petty to me.  i am a "casual" gamer.  i have shift work (schedule changes every 2 days) a wife who is pregnant, and 2 kids already.  i play as much as i can without inciting threats of divorce from the wife and doing things with my kids and living my life.
<br />

<br />
i JUST got my VT key this week.  i JUST got my PoJ trials done for progression, lol.  i have been playing EQ since a little before Luclin dropped.  my necro has been my main the entire time and i have played casually the entire time.  i can't wait to get into VT.  would it have been nice to be able to do LDoN's to get VT caliber gear:  HELLS YEAH  <img src="images/smiles/icon_eek.gif" alt="Shocked" border="0" />   am i gonna be mad if SOE puts it up for LDoN'ers to get for 2k pts:  HELLS NO <img src="images/smiles/icon_eek.gif" alt="Shocked" border="0" />   people pay for the game guys, to have fun.  not for what some other player's thoughts about them having an enjoyable experience.  
<br />

<br />
raiders have fun raiding. . . go raid.  don't be petty or jealous about some one getting a break.  i wouldn't be in a raiding guild now if i didn't have to.  i am on a PK server.  i LOVE to pk.  i may not be the best at it, but i am far from the worst.  the way PvP goes nowadays, skill is dust in the wind.  your gear pretty much determines the outcome of PvP (unless u r one of those heartless @$$hats who likes to train).  if u can't land a spell on someone then u can't fight them.  with that being the way it is, it's hard for people to dedicate the time it would take to fight a Time geared opponent on fair ground by gearing up for Time.  so due to the fact that i will probably never see Time in the near future i should stop playing EQ because i can't gear up like the Time guilds?<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=533103" target="_blank" class="postlink">Lich Revanche Vendetta</a>
