				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Last time I did VT, it was less than 4 hours from first kill to final AHR kill, 34ish players. Necro (me) runs screaming to blob1 and FDs. Rogue drags dead mage to me. Rez, CoH, and off we go.  Since then we have CoH mules spaced throughout the zone. 
<br />

<br />
Sadly, this means I may never get my splurt shoulders or ba4 stick since it takes too long to go that way.
<br />

<br />
Lootwise, VT is much better than bazaar stuff. The AHR necklace (35AC, 8 regen/FT/DS) is one of the better necks in the game. The focus effects and FT on items are all better than bazaar loot, and most of them are 100+HP. Not bad at all for gearing up to do time or GoD.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
