				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">How many pieces of loot does a clearing of VT yield?  30ish?  If you have a 30 person raid, even if it takes you 8 hours to clear, that's @ 1 upgrade per person per clearing.
<br />

<br />
Those same 30 people form 5 LDoN groups and spend 8 hours doing Normal LDoN's for 51 points each (I say normal, because if your group is getting upgrades in VT, you're going to have trouble winning Hard LDoN's).  That's @ 400 points for each person.  Have you seen the 400 point gear on LDoN merchants?  Not exactly VT - level.
<br />

<br />
...how is this as good as VT again?<br />_________________<br />Animocity S'eething
